Small Foot droogrek

Small Foot drying rack

Would you like to help your mom or dad hang the laundry? Then from now on you'll have your own drying rack. It is specially made for toddlers and preschoolers so that they can access it at the right height. Ideal for all small children!

Gender: junior
Material: wood
